DELLA: So?
DONALD: No sign of the guy.

1:13:24.483 --> 1:13:26.275
Did you get a name?

1:13:26.860 --> 1:13:29.362
How about the apartment?
You find something?

1:13:30.155 --> 1:13:31.531
Nothing?

