last March.

1:13:37.079 --> 1:13:39.705
Neighbors say that
his nephew stays there
from time to time

1:13:39.790 --> 1:13:41.958
while the probate
is being worked out.

1:13:42.042 --> 1:13:43.751
Except he doesn't
have a nephew.

1:13:43.836 --> 1:13:45.878
You're catching on fast.

1:13:46.755 --> 1:13:49.507
Cal, I thought we had
an understanding.

1:13:49.591 --> 1:13:51.342
You were supposed to share
your information with us.

1:13:51.427 --> 1:13:52.427
Do you remember that?

1:13:52.511 --> 1:13:56.973
Don, I went there
to talk to a guy named
Fred Summers, right,

1:13:57.057 --> 1:13:58.599
who I now find
out is deceased.

1:13:58.684 --> 1:14:00.351
