Just happened to
be there, huh?

1:14:03.814 --> 1:14:05.273
Yeah.

1:14:05.441 --> 1:14:06.983
Now, do you mind
if I get back
on with my story?

1:14:07.067 --> 1:14:09.569
It's not a story.
It's a case!

1:14:09.653 --> 1:14:13.489
And... And just so you know,
a girl by the name
of Mandi Brokaw,

1:14:13.574 --> 1:14:16.367
16, junkie,
turned up dead tonight.

1:14:17.369 --> 1:14:19.203
Probable homicide.

1:14:20.456 --> 1:14:22.206
She look familiar?

1:14:22.708 --> 1:14:23.958
We got her fingerprints
off of those

1:14:24.042 --> 1:14:26.419
surveillance photos
you so kindly gave us.

1:14:31.216 --> 1:14:34.260
Hello, I'm Rhonda Silver.

1:14:35.971 --> 1:14:39.640
Like I said,
that's what he called
"being in committee."

1:14:42.102 --> 1:14:43.978
I know you got shot
at last night,

1:14:44.062 --> 1:14:45.855
and I know I should be making
you a nice cup of cocoa,

1:14:45.939 --> 1:14:48.232
but I'm just so bloody angry!

1:14:48.317 --> 1:14:51.986
I mean, the decision,
I'm assuming, was that
this was not news.

1:14:52.863 --> 1:14:54.906
We... Look, we didn't...
We were worried that...

1:14:54.990 --> 1:14:57.575
It was my call, Cam.
All right?

1:14:57.659 --> 1:14:59.702
I didn't, and I don't
believe her.

1:14:59.870 --> 1:15:02.079
